div.div: Zero no Tsukaima: Princesses no Rondo
Action, Adventure, Comedy, Ecchi, Fantasy, Romance

Following Saito's heroic actions in the War with Albion in season two, Saito & Louise return to Tristain, only to have the runes which bind Saito & Louise disappear. Saito & Louise struggle with a relationship no longer defined as Master & Familiar, as they search for an Elf who has the power to restore the dead to life, and may hold the key to understanding Saito's loss of the Gandalfr's power.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Genjitsu Shugi Yuusha no Oukoku Saikenki Part 2

The second part of Genjitsu Shugi Yuusha no Oukoku Saikenki. Summoned to a fantasy world, Kazuya Souma is ruling a kingdom with a nontraditional (and very human) route of administrative reform. Hes tackling food shortages, mastering dark magic, and dazzling a few ladies along the way. Despite his latest good intentions, Kazuya breaks the ban on war to defeat a military dictatorship. Now, he must answer to the Gran Chaos Empires idealistic leaderuh oh. (Source: Funimation)
